        },
        "content": "This dashboard is environment-based, aggregating all the container apps in an environment. \n\n1. The [Azure Monitor data source is enabled](https://learn.microsoft.com/azure/managed-grafana/how-to-data-source-plugins-managed-identity?tabs=azure-portal).\n2. The time range is correct.\n\nRead more about monitoring your Azure Container Apps [here](https://learn.microsoft.com/azure/container-apps/observability).",
